scene.message:
Maki: So the real me{nl}
imagined everyone at{nl}
this school too, huh?{waitkey}What a strange feeling...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: The entrance to the{nl}
so-called Avidya World{nl}
is the library.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: This school and town,{nl}
once I killed Kandori,{nl}
I'd have no use for them...{waitkey}Or so I thought...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: {ctl07:1},{nl}
do you like school?{waitkey}{clearbox}I... used to think it was{nl}
a dull place. But now I{nl}
love it...{waitkey}It's where I met everyone...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: {ctl07:1},{nl}
do you care for school?{waitkey}{clearbox}I... once thought it{nl}
a tedious place.{nl}
But now I adore it...{waitkey}It's where I met everyone...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Y'know, I actually{nl}
kinda like school.{nl}
I'm hopeless at studying,{waitkey}but grades aren't everything.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl0f:1},{nl}
you like school?{nl}
Ayase kinda likes it.{waitkey}You can do your own thing!{waitkey}{ret}
